U.S. GLASS, INC.LICENSE #847943





































Background photo of Zinkin Fresno.US Glass 2006



US Glass, Inc. rated in the Top 50 glaziers in the USA in Glass Magazine 2008!

USG is soon to be one of the few accredited NACC Firms on the West Coast!!












MISSION STATEMENTUS Glass, Inc. Strives To Provide The Most Comprehensive Glazing Solutions To Meet The Ever-Changing Demands Of Today'S Dynamic Building Envelopes. As The Demand For More Technically Oriented And Energy Efficient And Even Energy Producing Facades Grows, US Glass, Inc. Is There To Provide The Expertise To Design, Engineer, And Install Your Project.

EXPERTISECurtainwalls (Stick And Unitized), Storefronts, Windows, Entrance Systems, Point Supported Glass Walls, Glass Canopies, Sunshades, Skylights, Rain Screen Systems (Including Terra Cotta And Phenolic), Panels (Plate, Acm, Textured).

ABOUT U.S. GLASS INCThank You For Visiting Our Site To Learn About Our Company. We Are A Union Commercial Glazing Contractor Servicing All Of Northern California.  We Take Pride In Our Ability To Work With Owners, Architects And General Contractors To Deliver The Project They Envision, On Time And Within Budget.We Have Extensive Experience In: Commercial Office Buildings, Education And Research, Hospitals And Medical Office Buildings, Retail And Interiors, Airports, Museums, Mixed Use As Well As DOE And DOD Projects, Blast Systems, OSHPD, DSA, Design-Build, LEED Certification And Remedial Projects.In The Future, We Hope That We Can Be Your Commercial Glazing Contractor Of Choice, And Would Be Pleased To Assist You On Design, Budgets, Pre-Construction, Quotations And Value Engineering On Your Projects. 


